OL,3,CPark cordoned off as police
OL,4,Cinvestigate serious sexual assault
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FA park in the centre of St Austell has
OL,8,Fbeen cordoned off as police
OL,9,Finvestigate reports of a serious
OL,10,Fsexual assault on a man.
OL,12,FIt was reported to have happened in
OL,13,FLinear Park, Longpark Way, at around
OL,14,F11pm on Monday 1 June.
OL,16,FOfficers from Devon and Cornwall
OL,17,FPolice say their enquiries are
OL,18,Fcurrently ongoing and there was a
OL,19,Flarge police presence in the area on
OL,20,FTuesday morning.
